      <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
         <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
         <p>Includes master tapes, phonograph records, and compact disks of various Cornell a cappella groups, including Cayuga's Waiters, Touchtones, Class Notes, Nothing But Treble and Hangovers.</p>
      </scopecontent>
